<cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0005a" xml:id="I01.0002.0005a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0005a00" type="honorific"/><cb:docNumber>No. 2</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0005a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>姚伯多等造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0005a00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一　碑陽</cb:mulu><head>之一　碑陽</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0005a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0005a0101">夫大道幽玄。以妙寄為宗。靈教<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">沾</unclear>澤。以<note n="0005001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30308"/>＝虛【史】</note><note n="0005001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30308"/>【佛拓】，虛【史】</note><app n="0005001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30308"/></rdg></app>寂為<note n="0005002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30355"/>＝所【史】</note><note n="0005002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30355"/>【佛拓】，所【史】</note><app n="0005002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30355"/></rdg></app>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">是</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">以</unclear>群方。而功不在
<lb ed="I" n="0005a02" type="honorific"/>己。生成萬物。不以存私為　稱。故　能苞羅六合。而品類咸熙。纖介通
<lb ed="I" n="0005a03" type="honorific"/>微。而感物不彫。經云。大道如　　　　　昧。而研之者明。至言若訥。而尋之
<lb ed="I" n="0005a04" type="honorific"/>者<note n="0005003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30356"/>＝辨【史】</note><note n="0005003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30356"/>【佛拓】，辨【史】</note><app n="0005003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">辨</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30356"/></rdg></app>。故真文彌梵。非高何以可宗。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">李</unclear>　　耳和生。非玄教<note n="0005a0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【原】【史】</note><app n="0005a0401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】 【史】">旡</rdg></app>以合空。<note n="0005004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">欝＝鬱【史】</note><note n="0005004" resp="ihp" type="mod">欝【佛拓】，鬱【史】</note><app n="0005004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鬱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">欝</rdg></app>陵<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">齊</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0005a05" type="honorific"/>禪。以致其真。當今世道。教紛群惑茲　　甚。假道亂真。群聚為媚。大道之□
<lb ed="I" n="0005a06" type="honorific"/>清<app type="star" corresp="#0005001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30308"/></rdg></app>唯真素。為潔練身。<note n="0005005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30357"/>＝剋【史】</note><note n="0005005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30357"/>【佛拓】，剋【史】</note><app n="0005005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剋</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30357"/></rdg></app>脩大道之本。　有北地姚伯多兄弟等。承帝舜之
<lb ed="I" n="0005a07" type="honorific"/>苗冑。珠紫<note n="0005006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30358"/>＝奕【史】</note><note n="0005006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30358"/>【佛拓】，奕【史】</note><app n="0005006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">奕</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30358"/></rdg></app>世。仰論士<note n="0005007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30359"/>＝爵【史】</note><note n="0005007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30359"/>【佛拓】，爵【史】</note><app n="0005007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">爵</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30359"/></rdg></app>。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">書</unclear>不可訖。九　族雍<note n="0005008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30354"/>＝穆【史】</note><note n="0005008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30354"/>【佛拓】，穆【史】</note><app n="0005008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">穆</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30354"/></rdg></app>。貞　素清潔。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">略</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">肅</unclear>至孝。通
<lb ed="I" n="0005a08" type="honorific"/><note n="0005009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30360"/>＝於【史】</note><note n="0005009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30360"/>【佛拓】，於【史】</note><app n="0005009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30360"/></rdg></app>神明。<note n="0005010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30375"/>＝望【史】</note><note n="0005010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30375"/>【佛拓】，望【史】</note><app n="0005010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">望</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30375"/></rdg></app><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">標</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">青</unclear>族。雅量淵廓。神心肅悮。發自天然。<note n="0005011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30361"/>＝雖【史】</note><note n="0005011" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30361"/>【佛拓】，雖【史】</note><app n="0005011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">雖</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30361"/></rdg></app>形寄時俗。超然<note n="0005012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30366"/>＝遠【史】</note><note n="0005012" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30366"/>【佛拓】，遠【史】</note><app n="0005012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30366"/></rdg></app>敬。乃自
<lb ed="I" n="0005a09" type="honorific"/><app type="star" corresp="#0005005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剋</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30357"/></rdg></app>削。內懷歡<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">心</unclear>。<app type="star" corresp="#0005009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30360"/></rdg></app>大代太和廿年歲在丙子九月辛酉朔四日甲子。姚伯
<lb ed="I" n="0005a10" type="honorific"/>多。伯龍。定　龍。伯養。天虎<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">等</unclear>。上為帝主。下為七祖眷屬。敬造皇老君文石
<lb ed="I" n="0005a11" type="honorific"/>像一軀。<note n="0005013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30362"/>＝營【史】</note><note n="0005013" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30362"/>【佛拓】，營【史】</note><app n="0005013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">營</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30362"/></rdg></app>構莊飾。　極工匠之奇彫。隱起形<note n="0005014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30363"/>＝圖【史】</note><note n="0005014" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30363"/>【佛拓】，圖【史】</note><app n="0005014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30363"/></rdg></app>。<note n="0005015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30317"/>＝瑍【史】</note><note n="0005015" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30317"/>【佛拓】，瑍【史】</note><app n="0005015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瑍</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30317"/></rdg></app>若真容。現<app type="star" corresp="#0005009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30360"/></rdg></app>今世。綺錯
<lb ed="I" n="0005a12" type="honorific"/>盡窮巧之剬。脩奉清顏。有若真對。非夫道協幽宗。理會亡言。焉能若此者。
<lb ed="I" n="0005a13" type="honorific"/><note n="0005016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">亐＝于【史】</note><note n="0005016" resp="ihp" type="mod">亐【佛拓】，于【史】</note><app n="0005016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">于</lem><rdg wit="【原】">亐</rdg></app>時奉敬之徒。欽太極以興觀。信悮之賓。<app type="star" corresp="#0005010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">望</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30375"/></rdg></app>玄門而<note n="0005017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30364"/>＝喪【史】</note><note n="0005017" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30364"/>【佛拓】，喪【史】</note><app n="0005017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">喪</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30364"/></rdg></app>偶。不勝欣躍之至。
<lb ed="I" n="0005a14" type="honorific"/>即而頌之。其辭曰。　　　芒芒太上。<note n="0005018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30365"/>＝疊【史】</note><note n="0005018" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30365"/>【佛拓】，疊【史】</note><app n="0005018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">疊</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30365"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0005018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">疊</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30365"/></rdg></app>幽微。<app type="star" corresp="#0005009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30360"/></rdg></app>矣皇老。誕精云湄。純<note n="0005019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30392"/>＝風【史】</note><note n="0005019" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30392"/>【佛拓】，風【史】</note><app n="0005019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">風</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30392"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0005a15" type="honorific"/>漸<note n="0005020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">皼＝鼓【史】</note><note n="0005020" resp="ihp" type="mod">皼【佛拓】，鼓【史】</note><app n="0005020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鼓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">皼</rdg></app>。品物沾暉。非至非成。熟啟<note n="0005021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB17851"/>＝冥【史】</note><note n="0005021" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB17851"/>【佛拓】，冥【史】</note><app n="0005021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">冥</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB17851"/></rdg></app>機。　洸洸尹生。妙契玄理。<app type="star" corresp="#0005012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30366"/></rdg></app>其城都。皓
<lb ed="I" n="0005a16" type="honorific"/><note n="0005022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30367"/>＝變【史】</note><note n="0005022" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30367"/>【佛拓】，變【史】</note><app n="0005022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">變</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30367"/></rdg></app>素起。微言既暢。萬累都止。陳文五千。功不在己。沖<app type="star" corresp="#0005001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30308"/></rdg></app>纏<note n="0005023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30368"/>＝邈【史】</note><note n="0005023" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30368"/>【佛拓】，邈【史】</note><app n="0005023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邈</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30368"/></rdg></app>。如昧俞深。不
<lb ed="I" n="0005a17" type="honorific"/>知其誰。像帝先人。化治西域。流波東秦。至感無其崇之者。因　既建石像。
<lb ed="I" n="0005a18" type="honorific"/><app type="star" corresp="#0005014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30363"/></rdg></app><note n="0005024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30316"/>＝藻【史】</note><note n="0005024" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30316"/>【佛拓】，藻【史】</note><app n="0005024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">藻</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30316"/></rdg></app>靈仙。在軒雲遘。岳峙霄間。莊麗嚴飾。妙觀閑　閑。髣髴神儀。載揚真
<lb ed="I" n="0005a19" type="honorific"/>賢。　濟濟川原。雍<app type="star" corresp="#0005008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">穆</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30354"/></rdg></app>開關。俄　俄風流。君子　交<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">齊</unclear>。降生哲　人。敘此熟
<lb ed="I" n="0005a20" type="honorific"/>資。清為時範。動為世師。非唯立德。　政化是妣。其妣唯何。唯政是匡。其政
<lb ed="I" n="0005a21" type="honorific"/>唯何。<note n="0005025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30370"/>＝柔【史】</note><note n="0005025" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30370"/>【佛拓】，柔【史】</note><app n="0005025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">柔</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30370"/></rdg></app>而能<note n="0005026" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30369"/>＝剛【史】</note><note n="0005026" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30369"/>【佛拓】，剛【史】</note><app n="0005026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30369"/></rdg></app>。造立石像。德立彌章。唯我皇老。与日　　齊光。伯多。伯龍。
<lb ed="I" n="0005a22" type="honorific"/>姚定龍。姚伯養。姚天□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">從</unclear>始供養。千載不<note n="0005027" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30371"/>＝忘【史】</note><note n="0005027" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30371"/>【佛拓】，忘【史】</note><app n="0005027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">忘</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30371"/></rdg></app>。壽身捨身。道<note n="0005028" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">炁＝氣【史】</note><note n="0005028" resp="ihp" type="mod">炁【佛拓】，氣【史】</note><app n="0005028"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">氣</lem><rdg wit="【原】">炁</rdg></app>將自。如此種福。
<lb ed="I" n="0005a23" type="honorific"/>□□萇入天堂。子<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">孫</unclear>□□後更煩昌。後人見之。供養<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">如</unclear>常。若當不信。□□</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
