<lb ed="I" n="0005b08" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0005b09" type="honorific"/>清信王<note n="0005029" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">軄＝職【史】</note><note n="0005029" resp="ihp" type="mod">軄【佛拓】，職【史】</note><app n="0005029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">職</lem><rdg wit="【原】">軄</rdg></app>女供養</p>
