<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0005c01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0005c0101">願造功者就。脩德者成。殖果有因。因中果生。信者善<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">終</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">從</unclear>明
<lb ed="I" n="0005c02" type="honorific"/>至明。福<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">來</unclear>照果。果以<app type="star" corresp="#0005015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瑍</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30317"/></rdg></app>榮。<app type="star" corresp="#0005001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30308"/></rdg></app>中遊<note n="0005030" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30349"/>＝翔【史】</note><note n="0005030" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30349"/>【佛拓】，翔【史】</note><app n="0005030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">翔</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30349"/></rdg></app>。梵音希聲。神仙為友。歷
<lb ed="I" n="0005c03" type="honorific"/>觀玉京。捨俗就道。貴在心精。　願星宿群<note n="0005031" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30350"/>＝僚【史】</note><note n="0005031" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30350"/>【佛拓】，僚【史】</note><app n="0005031"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">僚</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30350"/></rdg></app>。牧守令長。以德
<lb ed="I" n="0005c04" type="honorific"/>導民。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">立</unclear>條眾備。處物理均。善教既舒。民<note n="0005032" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30351"/>＝樂【史】</note><note n="0005032" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30351"/>【佛拓】，樂【史】</note><app n="0005032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">樂</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30351"/></rdg></app>仰遵。邑景寧太。雅
<lb ed="I" n="0005c05" type="honorific"/>詠日新。道能濟物。信与宜純。　坦坦原隰。仁義可親。左平右
<lb ed="I" n="0005c06" type="honorific"/>大。北<note n="0005033" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30352"/>＝顧【史】</note><note n="0005033" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30352"/>【佛拓】，顧【史】</note><app n="0005033"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顧</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30352"/></rdg></app>頻山。眾泉合流。注<app type="star" corresp="#0005016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">于</lem><rdg wit="【原】">亐</rdg></app>茲川。洸洸濟濟。仁林俠邊。<app type="star" corresp="#0005008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">穆</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30354"/></rdg></app>〃
<lb ed="I" n="0005c07" type="honorific"/>英儒。得生<app type="star" corresp="#0005016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">于</lem><rdg wit="【原】">亐</rdg></app>閒。神像功就。<app type="star" corresp="#0005009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30360"/></rdg></app>茲有緣。安<app type="star" corresp="#0005002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30355"/></rdg></app>仁理。不<note n="0005034" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30353"/>＝歪【史】</note><note n="0005034" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30353"/>【佛拓】，歪【史】</note><app n="0005034"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">歪</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30353"/></rdg></app>不偏。其
<lb ed="I" n="0005c08" type="honorific"/>　<app type="star" corresp="#0005014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30363"/></rdg></app>玉瑩。綺飾交連。既建岳峙。与山齊連。<note n="0005035" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30374"/>＝兆【史】</note><note n="0005035" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30374"/>【佛拓】，兆【史】</note><app n="0005035"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">兆</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30374"/></rdg></app>劫不移。往來
<lb ed="I" n="0005c09" type="honorific"/>　神仙。<app type="star" corresp="#0005002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30355"/></rdg></app>願成□。壽命萇延。</p>
</cb:div>
