<lb ed="I" n="0005f01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0005f0101">願<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">帝</unclear>主<note n="0005036" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30393"/>＝國【史】</note><note n="0005036" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30393"/>【佛拓】，國【史】</note><app n="0005036"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">國</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30393"/></rdg></app>王以□□物。敷教濟濟。休問<app type="star" corresp="#0005012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30366"/></rdg></app>彰。邊　<note n="0005037" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30372"/>＝夷【史】</note><note n="0005037" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30372"/>【佛拓】，夷【史】</note><app n="0005037"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">夷</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30372"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0005f02" type="honorific"/>賓伏。<note n="0005038" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">灾＝災【史】</note><note n="0005038" resp="ihp" type="mod">灾【佛拓】，災【史】</note><app n="0005038"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">災</lem><rdg wit="【原】">灾</rdg></app>害自<note n="0005039" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30373"/>＝亡【史】</note><note n="0005039" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30373"/>【佛拓】，亡【史】</note><app n="0005039"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亡</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30373"/></rdg></app>。德流<app type="star" corresp="#0005035"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">兆</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30374"/></rdg></app>庶。善瑞榛祥。民<app type="star" corresp="#0005032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">樂</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30351"/></rdg></app>貞信。　臣
<lb ed="I" n="0005f03" type="honorific"/>節忠良。道協靈應。族延未央。以道為基。与仙相　<app type="star" corresp="#0005010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">望</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30375"/></rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0005f04" type="honorific"/>願道民姚伯多。三宗五祖。七世父　　母。前亡後<note n="0005040" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30376"/>＝死【史】</note><note n="0005040" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30376"/>【佛拓】，死【史】</note><app n="0005040"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">死</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30376"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0005f05" type="honorific"/>眷屬。若在三徒。速得解脫。得<app type="star" corresp="#0005012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30366"/></rdg></app>　　<note n="0005041" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB18853"/>＝離【史】</note><note n="0005041" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB18853"/>【佛拓】，離【史】</note><app n="0005041"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">離</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB18853"/></rdg></app>囚徒幽執之
<lb ed="I" n="0005f06" type="honorific"/>苦。上昇南宮神鄉之土。若更下生。侯王為父。當令伯
<lb ed="I" n="0005f07" type="honorific"/>多父母兄弟。妻息大小。均心同信。尊道為主。學以萇
<lb ed="I" n="0005f08" type="honorific"/>生。神仙為侶。福慶隆昌。子孫斯与。<app type="star" corresp="#0005002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30355"/></rdg></app>願<app type="star" corresp="#0005005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剋</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30357"/></rdg></app>成。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">若</unclear>□神
<lb ed="I" n="0005f09" type="honorific"/>□。如此種福。功德□□□□</p>
